{"tid":2118000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英新藥有效治武肺 減八成重症","createTime":"2020-07-21T08:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T10:24:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3d0e4d01a830b64ef2ecf3b6eb17f3e82d6e37","tid":2118000,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:02:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200721/MM5JIRUNH7SSDKEGR4KB4UROFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200721%2FMM5JIRUNH7SSDKEGR4KB4UROFY%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=e66120b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200721%2FMM5JIRUNH7SSDKEGR4KB4UROFY%2F&h=f6f3a3fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200721/MM5JIRUNH7SSDKEGR4KB4UROFY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英新藥有效治武肺 減八成重症<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KNIjo3TqRQIS2lpYO3dI-Uk3rqU=/470x302/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PXO34HICWSQM4ARXLDFZXUDVVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKNIjo3TqRQIS2lpYO3dI-Uk3rqU%3D%2F470x302%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPXO34HICWSQM4ARXLDFZXUDVVI.jpg&h=1aaeee5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國小型製藥公司研發了有效治療武肺重症藥物。<br />\n<br />\n英國小型製藥公司Synairgen一種新藥物，在小型實驗中顯示對治療武漢肺炎有很大功效，能減少近八成病人接受深切治療以至死亡，醫學界指這是令人振奮的好消息。<br />\n<br />\n新藥由Synairgen和南安普敦大學共同研發，暫名「SNG001」，是以吸入式服用，內含干擾素beta。這種蛋白是免疫。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仍須大規模測試<br />\n<br />\n研究員在實驗向101名武肺病人作隨機試驗，其中一半服用安慰劑，結果發現服用該藥的病人，病情惡化至需要用呼吸機的機率少79%，而完全康復至可過正常生活的機率高一倍多。此外，服用安慰劑的病人有三人死亡，服用該藥的則沒有人死。<br />\n<br />\n這項研究尚未受同行評審，專家指尚需要更大規模的測試，在較大樣本得出的結果有可能指藥效沒那麼大。曼徹斯特大學免。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/英國《泰晤士報》"},{"pid":"74140f1887c330ac7b82adef00bacd9dcabd4fd6","tid":2118000,"uid":156327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:03:03.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"e4ec2d09d70cc9cc5242e25f2846c97607a2cb7c","tid":2118000,"uid":258770,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:04:21.000Z","msg":"支針筒抽撚哂d空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7640a16c04ae4efb09638dfb678ea6f6e8d5b986","tid":2118000,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:05:17.000Z","msg":"Southampton U <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f33b912440405df263d61a79530e18eb03494d","tid":2118000,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:05:23.000Z","msg":"唉 又要乜測試物測試，<br />\n<br />\n年頭有隻藥，去到家下都未放出尼。<br />\n<br />\n試到依家都未試完。"},{"pid":"84cbf8572bbf39d892023737263e37f0bd3f9239","tid":2118000,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4ec2d09d70cc9cc5242e25f2846c97607a2cb7c","tid":2118000,"uid":258770,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:04:21.000Z","msg":"支針筒抽撚哂d空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:07:11.000Z","msg":"福圖係setup比記者用咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bd7ec71cab6d358e699c15f40df921ce03b849","tid":2118000,"uid":61327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:07:56.000Z","msg":"今晚升 大奇蹟日"},{"pid":"18159f818d03cd27f5e65392b31bb71d3d623a5f","tid":2118000,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:08:14.000Z","msg":"如制裁香港<br />\n<br />\n香港會否無得用？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只可以食雙黃蓮?"},{"pid":"f2a32c71938161383539d2b96d2be4701bca627c","